    "Users can communicate with LLMs and control the planning process in (A) Chat view by selecting the tasks or setting the decomposition plan.",
    "The generated visualization and insights from LLMs are updated in (B) Visualization view.",
    "Task flow view (C) visualizes the task planning structure and allows users to control the analysis process.",
    "When a task is completed, users check the data exploration situation in the Data table with table lens (D).Second, assess if the task requires further data mining or visualization methods (e.g., regression, clustering) to extract deeper insights.",
